==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Miscount
<hw>Mis*count"</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Cf. F.
<ets>m⟦eacute⟧compte</ets> error, OF. <ets>mesconte</ets>.]</ety>
<sn>1.</sn> <def>An erroneous counting.</def>⟦br⟧
